title: 14: Why I Stopped the Podcast for 3 Months
description: Long time no see, LITERALLY. We know what you're all thinking, holy sh!t Sadie is finally back, but this dumb b!txh has the worst consistency in the podcast scene. TRUE ... but there's a reason Sadie was actually in a little cobweb and couldn't get out of it. Listen in to hear why Sadie LEGALLY had to stop her podcast for a little while.
